Information
------------------------------

Stan Lees Superhumans: Season 3
On Stan Lee's Superhumans 3 from H2, Stan Lee and the World's Most Flexible Man, Daniel Browning-Smith, travel the world testing the claims of real people who declare they have genuine superpowers.




10)  Ultimate Super Team 
Creating teams of comic book heroes requires a combination of incredible but unique superpowers. This time Daniel meets four people with totally separate powers...but could they be ultimate team of real life superhumans?
